00:22:12,090 --> 00:22:13,030
interesting spaces.

403
00:22:14,011 --> 00:22:17,352
Highly interconnected spaces, horizontally and vertically,

404
00:22:18,492 --> 00:22:19,813
are what are interesting.

405
00:22:19,893 --> 00:22:22,454
Locations that have many entrance and exit points are

406
00:22:22,494 --> 00:22:22,874
interesting.

407
00:22:22,974 --> 00:22:24,514
Interconnected spaces are interesting.

408
00:22:26,115 --> 00:22:28,336
And every problem is going to have multiple solutions.

409
00:22:31,403 --> 00:22:36,046
Okay. So I was laying down these filters and commandments and

