00:30:39,427 --> 00:30:40,408
ended up having to cut.

565
00:30:41,048 --> 00:30:43,570
But that mission showed the potential of the game.

566
00:30:43,590 --> 00:30:45,431
We hacked in everything that we knew we

567
00:30:45,491 --> 00:30:46,412
wanted the player to do.

568
00:30:46,432 --> 00:30:47,973
It was totally hacked.

569
00:30:49,174 --> 00:30:51,595
And we saw a bunch of stuff that didn't work.

