00:30:51,635 --> 00:30:53,296
That's the power of proto missions,

571
00:30:53,716 --> 00:30:54,857
as we called them back then.

572
00:30:55,697 --> 00:30:56,938
Our performance was abysmal.

573
00:30:57,678 --> 00:31:01,040
We knew we'd have to cut our maps up into smaller chunks.

574
00:31:01,380 --> 00:31:03,021
The skill system that I came up with,

