00:36:43,912 --> 00:36:49,455
to have a deep sim and allow fighting, sneaking and talking. We had to layer all that stuff in

668
00:36:49,515 --> 00:36:49,935
on top.

669
00:36:50,938 --> 00:36:55,441
It worked, but we ended up faking a lot of stuff, just to

670
00:36:55,481 --> 00:36:56,922
be frank.

671
00:36:57,022 --> 00:36:59,503
Deus Ex, there's a lot of smoke and mirrors going on

