00:37:12,792 --> 00:37:13,773
did hurt the game some.

678
00:37:18,632 --> 00:37:19,793
I don't remember what I was going to say here.

679
00:37:20,433 --> 00:37:20,753
Okay.

680
00:37:22,054 --> 00:37:23,275
I guess for the most part,

